The paper proposes a deep hashing algorithm for efficient information retrieval, which involves deep learning techniques and optimization methods. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the loss functions and optimization strategies, which are common topics in machine learning and optimization, suggesting that cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category. The paper focuses on information retrieval, which falls under the category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of large-scale datasets and the evaluation of the proposed method, which are relevant to cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
